OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,FThe purpose of the investigation was
OL,7,Fto finally decide a true figure of how
OL,8,Fmany people died during the German
OL,9,FOccupation and to, in the words of
OL,10,FLord Eric Pickles, "provide dignity to
OL,11,Fthe dead and peace to the people of
OL,12,FAlderney, who continue to remember
OL,13,Fthem".
