OL,3,CInvestigation reveals true extent of
OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,FHe added: "Claims of mass murder that
OL,7,Fanywhere else would be checked
OL,8,Fcarefully have been accepted at face
OL,9,Fvalue. A letter from Reichsfuhrer-SS
OL,10,FHimmler published decades ago is
OL,11,Fpresented as an "exclusive"
OL,12,Fbreakthrough. Third or fourth-hand
OL,13,Ftestimonies of atrocities, without any
OL,14,Fsupporting evidence, are given as fact.
OL,16,F"Anyone with the temerity to question
OL,17,Fsuch assertions is accused of being
OL,18,Fpart of a 'cover-up'.
