OL,3,CInvestigation reveals true extent of
OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,F"What happened on Alderney was bad
OL,7,Fenough with its brutality, sadism and
OL,8,Fmurder, without the need for
OL,9,Fembellishment."
OL,11,FThe review found that the highest
OL,12,Fnumber of deaths occurred between 1942
OL,13,Fand 1944 and most of the victims were
OL,14,FEastern European.
OL,16,FMore than 7,000 slave workers were
OL,17,Fshipped to Alderney during the
OL,18,FOccupation to build fortifications for
OL,19,FHitler's Atlantic Wall.
