OL,3,CInvestigation reveals true extent of
OL,4,CNazi atrocities in Alderney
OL,6,FThese people were largely kept in
OL,7,Flabour camps where they endured
OL,8,Fstarvation, long working hours,
OL,9,Fbeatings, maiming, torture and, in
OL,10,Fsome cases, executions.
OL,12,FResearchers have found evidence that
OL,13,Fsuggests, on a few occasions, bodies
OL,14,Fwere even dumped into the sea.
OL,16,FHowever, claims that Alderney
OL,17,Fconstituted a 'mini-Auschwitz' remain
OL,18,Funsubstantiated and there is no
OL,19,Fevidence that the island ever housed
OL,20,Fan extermination camp.
